<h1>Your RoboMix cocktail:</h1>
<p>
  A <%= @robo_format.name %>-format cocktail
</p>
With:
<ul>
  <li>
    1.5 oz <%= @robo_liquor.name %>
  </li>

  <li>
    0.75 oz <%= @robo_sweetener.name %>
  </li>

  <li>
    2 dashes <%= @robo_bitters.name %>
  </li>
</ul>

<h3>
  Suggested technique
</h3>
<p>
  In a mixing glass, add <%= @robo_liquor.name.downcase %>, <%= @robo_sweetener.name.downcase %>, and <%= @robo_bitters %> over ice. Stir for 20 seconds or to your preferred coldness, then strain into a rocks glass over ice. Garnish with a citrus twist of your choice and/or a maraschino cherry.
</p>